fields.description: The name of the Azure storage location where the export is stored. This only applies to exports stored in your own Azure storage location. The azureBlobContainer property is deprecated and will stop returning data on April 30th, 2023.
fields.name: AzureBlobContainer

fields.description: The SAS token for the Azure storage location.  This only applies to exports stored in your own Azure storage location. The azureBlobToken property is deprecated and will stop returning data on April 30, 2023.
fields.name: AzureBlobToken

fields.description: The description provided for the export.
fields.name: Description

fields.description: Contains the properties for an export file metadata, including downloadUrl, fileName, and size. If you export to an Azure storage location, this property returns empty.
fields.name: ExportFileMetadata

fields.description: The options provided for the export. For more information, see reviewSet: export. Possible values are: originalFiles, text, pdfReplacement, fileInfo, tags. The fileInfo member is deprecated and will stop returning data on April 30, 2023. Going forward, the summary and load file are always included.
fields.name: ExportOptions

fields.description: The options provided that specify the structure of the export. For more information, see reviewSet: export. Possible values are: none, directory, pst.
fields.name: ExportStructure

fields.description: The output folder ID. The outputFolderId property is deprecated and will stop returning data on April 30, 2023.
fields.name: OutputFolderId

fields.description: The name provided for the export.
fields.name: OutputName

fields.description: Review set from where documents are exported.
fields.name: ReviewSet

fields.description: The review set query that is used to filter the documents for export.
fields.name: ReviewSetQuery
